Required env var -

GIT_USERNAME
CERT_REPO
ROOT_PASSWORD
GIT_TOKEN
CERT_FILE

Before deploying any applications, please generate standalone cert and run ansible backup_cert
- sudo certbot certonly --standalone -d ur.domain.com
- ansible-playbook -i infraAutoVPS/ansible/inventory/hosts infraAutoVPS/ansible/playbooks/main.yaml --tags "ssl_management" --check

Apply/restore cert to server - run ansible restore_cert
- ansible-playbook -i infraAutoVPS/ansible/inventory/hosts infraAutoVPS/ansible/playbooks/main.yaml --tags "backup" --check